### Tests des routes API (extension VSCode "REST Client" ou "HTTP Client")
### Base URL
@base = http://localhost:4000/api
@token = COLLE_ICI_LE_TOKEN_RENVOYE_PAR_LOGIN

### Healthcheck
GET {{base}}/health

### Register
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pseudo": "Charlie",
  "email": "charlie@tcg.dev",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login (récupère le token, puis colle-le dans @token ci-dessus)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@tcg.dev",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Profil courant (protégé)
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Liste des cartes (publique, paginée)
GET {{base}}/cards?page=1&limit=20

### Recherche de cartes
GET {{base}}/cards?search=dragon&grade=3

### Détail d'une carte
GET {{base}}/cards/1

### Mes decks (protégé)
GET {{base}}/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Créer un deck (protégé)
POST {{base}}/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mon deck agressif",
  "cards": [
    { "cardId": 1, "quantity": 4 },
    { "cardId": 3, "quantity": 4 },
    { "cardId": 9, "quantity": 4 },
    { "cardId": 13, "quantity": 4 }
  ]
}

### Mon historique de parties (protégé)
GET {{base}}/games
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
